<Author>duckfoot
<Content>Lovely base for our stay. Wasn't sure what to expect from this hotel, but considered ourselves very lucky to stay there! We arrived very late on Friday night and were met with smiling reception staff and plenty of beer at the bar. Staying in Berlin is fantastic due to their wonderful transport system. We found the Aparthotel an der spree a great base for our stay. The meals were excellent, the rooms definitely comfortable and inviting and the free internet was a bonus! We are booking to return next year....loved Berlin and loved this hotel. 
